    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2311912/" class="title-link">我觉得有媒体曲解大家对这本书的热卖原因了</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2311912"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zengke/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1340455-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zengke/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">被山猪笑</span>
